div1.p: Territory of Washington County of Spokane}ss.

I, Kate W. Feuerbach Clerk of the District Court of the Territory of Washington, and for the First Fourth Judicial District thereof, do hereby certify that the above and foregoing is a true and correct copy of a writ of Habeas Corpus this day served on the Sheriff of Spokane in the above entitled cause, as the same now appears on file in my office.
In testimony whereof I have hereunto set my hand and affixed the seal of said Court, this 4th day of May, A.D. 1885 Kate W. Feuerbach Clerk. By R. Strobach Deputy.
